'''''John na John''''' ni [[Gana|firime yo muri Gana]] igaragaramo inshuti ebyiri bombi bitwaga John<ref>https://bg.listvote.com/lists/film/movies/58456860/actors</ref>. John umwe yashutse umugabo amugurisha zahabu mpimbano. Inshuti zombi zarimo zihunga n'amafaranga, ariko imodoka yabo yagenze nabi barara mu nzu y'abashyitsi<ref>https://viewghana.com/film-review-john-and-john-movie/</ref>. Igihe bakuraga amafaranga mu gikapu cyabo, yaguye hasi itera impungenge mu bashyitsi ndetse n'abakozi muri hoteri aho abantu bose bashakaga kwiba amafaranga<ref>https://www.ghmoviefreak.com/movie-review-john-john-imitation-vrs-creativity/</ref>     

Igishimishije, iyi filime niyo yagurishije cyane kurenza uko babikekaga, ariko yanze kwemerwa  muri Afrika yepfo  kuko hasohotse yo indi bisa yitwa Skeem yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Tim Greene mumwaka wa 2011<ref>https://www.pulse.com.gh/ece-frontpage/john-and-john-movie-south-african-movie-director-accuses-kofi-asamoah-of-plaigiarism/njndezj</ref>. 

Muri 2017 abanyamakuru ba Ghanain begereye Greene kugira ngo barebe ibyo Asamoah avuga ko yahawe uruhushya rwo guhuza iyo filimi<ref>https://answersafrica.com/20-best-ghanaian-movies-every-ghallywood-fan-should-watch.html</ref>, ariko we akaba atari ayifite. Asamoah yemeye kugura uburenganzira bwo gusubiramo, ariko ntiyigeze akurikiza amasezerano<ref>https://filmlinkafrica.com/en/2018/06/15/african-actors-ghanaian-john-dumelo-majid-michel-and-van-vicker/</ref>. Nta kirego cyemewe n'amategeko, kubera ko ikiguzi cyo gukurikirana urubanza rw'umutungo bwite mu by'ubwenge kirega Asamoah kitari kuba ingirakamaro<ref>https://www.ghanafilmindustry.com/watch-ghana-movies/</ref>.

